<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>87</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Khrihfami i lawm u, thinlung tak le aw in, Kan chimmi hi ngai hmanh u;
 Thawngtha! nihin ah Khrih a chuak cang Caw le laa a hmai an kun, Atu caw
 rawl einak kuang ah, A chuak cang Khamhtu, Nihin a chuak cang.

[V2]
 Khrihfami i lawm u, thinlung tak le aw in, Dong lo nuamhnak thawng nan
 theih, Lawm tuah! hi ca Khrih cu a chuak cang, Van cung innka cu a hun,
 Mi ca ah zungzal nuamhnak ah, Hi ca Khrih a chuak, Hi ca a chuak cang.

[V3]
 Khrihfami i lawm u, thinlung tak le aw in, Thlan zongnan tih ti lai
 lo, Daihnak! Khrih nih khamh awk a chuak cang, An auh nang le mi vialte,
 A umnak inn co awk caah, Khamhtu Khrih a chuak, Khamh awk a chuak cang.</lyrics>
<key>F</key>
<title>KHRIHFAMI I LAWM U CH87</title>
</song>